{"tid":2451563,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解one piece《海賊王》仲未被大陸禁播？","createTime":"2021-03-18T07:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T14:04:20.000Z","uid":365791,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bee09e34a648af75fdd45b145708401daf9d312c","tid":2451563,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:57:02.000Z","msg":"細個果陣睇唔明《海賊王》，點解海軍咁奸，海賊反而咁正義？大個再睇返先睇得明，《海賊王》完全係哩個世界嘅縮影，極權嘅醜陋完全係作者筆下描繪晒出黎 <br />\n<br />\n天龍人，擁有特權階級的貴族<br />\n＝共產黨，紅二代 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m5Oyy58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm5Oyy58.jpg&h=8b853266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界政府，腐敗的機構，打壓人民，放任貴族<br />\n＝腐敗的聯合國，放任極權國家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2jfEuEx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2jfEuEx.jpg&h=b00a764d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCP9，政府秘密殺人組織 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVwgwS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVwgwS3.jpg&h=bac3ff0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海軍，被貴族極權利用的軍事機構<br />\n＝3萬隻狗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GExWwS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGExWwS8.jpg&h=abc95f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QgL9EP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QgL9EP.jpg&h=9ae4a68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅賓細細個住嘅學者村被滅村，羅賓細個冇犯案但就被通緝，海軍話你係有罪就有罪<br />\n屠魔令＝滅族<br />\n<br />\n不過海軍入面都有正義嘅海軍，哈古瓦爾&middot;D&middot;薩烏羅協助羅賓逃避海軍追殺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9v5qdq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9v5qdq.jpg&h=e6d09226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YfGsDFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYfGsDFa.jpg&h=77569279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kjggw1C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjggw1C.jpg&h=c07b4dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七武海，海軍提拔嘅組織<br />\n＝勾結鄉黑 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzZNDyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzZNDyA.jpg&h=ebc75f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者筆下世界的寫照 <br />\n<br />\n集中營，人民被捉去勞改<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQ7obTG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQ7obTG.jpg&h=dfbfb5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ak4BwTH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAk4BwTH.jpg&h=386a3d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界政府的腐敗出現革命軍同海賊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHSC0OT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHSC0OT.jpg&h=9d459fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oyvUiAz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoyvUiAz.jpg&h=a98319bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有做海賊先可以自由自在<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vMHst0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vMHst0.jpg&h=8ecd03c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45aaed9cffc368e946f4ce3ce929bb5770e5d3ee","tid":2451563,"uid":291487,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"禁完又播返<br />\n禁到悶"},{"pid":"1610f2c525ef38896db9ff84c893ffc6370fb2c9","tid":2451563,"uid":40267,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"支那人眼中佢地係革命軍<br />\n世界政府同海軍係萬惡歐美帝國主義份子"},{"pid":"720d06277dbb829cba3ed72a06f2b57a173b4e89","tid":2451563,"uid":115579,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"背脊印住正義兩個字真係最大嘅反諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99bd8d9109284647640500d8182b3ed93be43e2","tid":2451563,"uid":115579,"